pullRequest.title: Azure Search Documents Performance Tests
pullRequest.bodyText:
Fixes #14308
This PR adds performance tests for azure-search-documents. The performance test scenarios are Autocomplete, Search, Suggest, and Document Indexing. The initial performance tests will only offer the ability to configure the number of documents in the index for autocomplete, search, and suggest and the number of documents in the index batch and the size of the document. In the future permutations of auto-completion, searching, and suggesting could be added to exercise more complex scenarios.

commit.message: azure-search-documents performance tests for autocomplete, search, suggest, and document indexing
